{"tid":177592,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪盼約曹星如河國榮做訪問 全港七百萬人喜極而泣","createTime":"2017-03-29T03:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:13:56.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1b196941a4d0d715fe413ee9b91d899705d920","tid":177592,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170328/photo/bkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170329055718\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170329055718&h=636e8514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人朱千雪今午到中環出席手機品牌活動，現在半工讀的朱千雪由於要上學關係，要一早起身打扮，放學再趕到現場，認真辛苦。剛拍竣劇集的她表示，暑假不打算再開劇，以便應付考試。她笑言自己將時間用盡，亦不覺得在男同學堆中有人有意向她展開追求：「大家都淨係掛住讀書，唔諗其他嘢。（冇時間拍拖？）依家科技咁發達，可以保持聯絡嘅，雖然我未有對象。」她稍後將應手機品牌之邀，四出訪問香港的本土感動事：「約緊曹星如同河國榮，仲可以同佢哋自拍，好期待呀。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170328/photo/bkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_03p.jpg?20170329055718\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20170329055718&h=ba55491b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為要返學，千雪話每日都過得好充實～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170328/photo/bkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_04p.jpg?20170329055718\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20170329055718&h=8b4d7e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSelfie呀呀呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170328/photo/bkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_05p.jpg?20170329055718\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170328154425075-0328_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20170329055718&h=0a681b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暑期唔打算打劇，專心學業～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0a62jr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0a62jr1.jpg&h=f7e8be87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天啊點解可以這麼正～"},{"pid":"08676733e219e7504f9b42f8080c25314c3ca177","tid":177592,"uid":25838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4811b92e9b49ac6ff1d61609788f9fe56b8095d4","tid":177592,"uid":72475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"見過真人<br />\n相差唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883a5d5435755a599acb1e491e6f16a35c241e7a","tid":177592,"uid":45931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"嗚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89d49307b8d42e4c13eeb2b0acd46732f72c6d2","tid":177592,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"著出show衫返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好有趣"},{"pid":"77c5548a73e80505e073bdd28ac1bf3355e3c4aa","tid":177592,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d37009ad3cad147f16146f229c06f2edcb1fe7e0","tid":177592,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過真人<br />\n相差唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真人仲靚d喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e25b4cead265fa82aa0523ff46c8e7efb90e8c","tid":177592,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/85j